<%= render "shared/navbar-home" %>
<div class="banner" style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.4),rgba(0,0,0,0.4)), url('./assets/images/banner.png');">
  <div class="container container-box">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="column">
        <div style="margin-bottom: 20px">
          <h1>Find unique micro coworking places in your street.</h1>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div style="margin-bottom: 20px">
            <%= form_tag spaces_path, class: "search-container", method: :get do %>
            <%= text_field_tag :location,
            params[:location],
            placeholder: "Where do you want to work?", class: "form-control search", autofocus: true
            %>
          </div>
          <div style="margin-bottom: 20px">
            <%= text_field_tag :start_date,
            params[:start_date],
            placeholder: "When do you want to start?", class: "form-control search", autofocus: true
            %>
          </div>
          <div style="margin-bottom: 20px">
            <%= text_field_tag :end_date,
            params[:end_date],
            placeholder: "When do you want to finish?", class: "form-control search", autofocus: true
            %>
          </div>
          <div class="input-group-append">
            <button class="btn btn-flat" type="submit">Submit</button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="column">
        <div class="checkboxes-home">
          <p><%= check_box_tag :space_type, 'Private spaces' %> Private spaces</p>
          <p><%= check_box_tag :space_type, 'Community spaces' %> Community spaces</p>
          <p><%= check_box_tag :space_type, 'Corporate spaces' %> Corporate spaces</p>
          <p><%= check_box_tag :space_type, 'Professional space' %> Professional spaces</p>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>


  <div class="home-container-1">
    <div>
      <h3>Explore myCO</h3>
      <p>myCO offers plenty of differnt home office and coworking variations - go and check them out. </p>
    </div>

    <div class="cards">
      <div class="card-category" style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.3), rgba(0,0,0,0.3)), url(https://raw.githubusercontent.com/lewagon/fullstack-images/master/uikit/breakfast.jpg)">
        Private spaces
      </div>

      <div class="card-category" style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.3), rgba(0,0,0,0.3)), url(https://raw.githubusercontent.com/lewagon/fullstack-images/master/uikit/lunch.jpg)">
        Community spaces
      </div>

      <div class="card-category" style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.3), rgba(0,0,0,0.3)), url(https://raw.githubusercontent.com/lewagon/fullstack-images/master/uikit/dinner.jpg)">
        Corporate spaces
      </div>

      <div class="card-category" style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.3), rgba(0,0,0,0.3)), url(https://raw.githubusercontent.com/lewagon/fullstack-images/master/uikit/dinner.jpg)">
        Professional spaces
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

<div class="home-container-2">
  <div>
    <h3>How does myCO work and whatâ€™s in for you?</h3>
    <p>myCO is designed to leverage existing spaces and create new communities in the local neighborhoods. For example, a private individual who has more space than he or she actually needs for his or her own home office can offer a home office space to a neighbor who has a need but little private space. In addition, operators of commercial coworking spaces, can achieve better occupancy of the workspaces they offer, by providing home office space to individuals who live nearby. In addition, companies that have a larger office building capacity than they actually need can rent out the excess workspace to private individuals through myCO. We're building on local synergies between individuals and individuals and businesses. Space is plentiful - it's just a question of how we use it.</p>
  </div>
  <%= image_tag('Big_Card.png') %>
</div>

<div class="home-container-3">
  <div>
    <h3>Private coworking spaces</h3>
    <p>Use the available private space we have. Learn more about your neighborhood and foster community as well.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="private-spaces">
    <% @private_spaces.limit(5).each do |space| %>
      <div class="card" style="width: 18rem;">
        <% if space.photo.attached? %>
          <%= cl_image_tag space.photo.key, crop: :fill %>
        <% end %>
        <div class="card-body">
          <h5 class="card-title"><%= space.title %></h5>
          <p class="card-text"><%= space.location %></p>
          <%= link_to "Continue", space_path(space.id, :location => params[:location]), class: "create btn btn-warning", style: "margin-top: 8px; border-radius: 50px"  %>
        </div>
      </div>
    <% end %>
  </div>
</div>

